Visualize invariant of integer rotation.
Uses:
     libpng and png++ - C++ wrapper for libpng. (Usually can be found in the repository).
     BOOST, including "option_parse".
     CMake as build system (not really needed).

Ugly, write-once code.

Compile flags are in the CMakeFIles.

Compilation (with CMake):

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake ../
$ make


Installation:
  Do not install it.

Running:
 use --help to see options. Everything is optional.
 Just run the executable and see result.